summary: Taylor, would you ever consider doing something like what Selena did today? It wouldn’t necessarily have to be a live because...
body:
Taylor, would you ever consider doing something like what Selena did today? It wouldn’t necessarily have to be a live because you’d get trolls with nasty agendas.. but I know we as the people who have stood by you would love the opportunity to ask you in real time about your art, things you’re inspired by, advice and just talk to you.

Honestly though we just love the commitment and relationship we have with you. So grateful @taylorswift
